{"tid":989620,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人自己同另一半都有情緒病","createTime":"2019-01-21T04:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T12:52:09.000Z","uid":205307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f23a5ea8da74a95f8677a8abfdafb55d8c49a6ac","tid":989620,"uid":205307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"可唔可以分享下平時點過同點配合<br />\n大家都去到最bad mood既時候會點<br />\n唔想成日一齊好似困獸鬥咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3240789b021d0d1067995ce746f09604465747","tid":989620,"uid":205307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:06:32.000Z","msg":"浪漫到一起惹絕症<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e6258b7b4be084c220e3ee83988bc07d5058f2","tid":989620,"uid":205307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:21:21.000Z","msg":"冇人？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a62026abe352b3ed0648516127fed587e130a72","tid":989620,"uid":205307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f33b6dca63bec97e08d58682f849e3832b1666","tid":989620,"uid":75707,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:59:03.000Z","msg":"好撚煩 做錯乜撚野都賴落自己有病到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf8f3c1af767c775782027bc485c5a25f35a25d","tid":989620,"uid":17245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:04:21.000Z","msg":"最撚慘係明明另一半迫到自己有情緒病<br />\n但睇醫生，社工，心理醫生都係著重話你有啲咩野問題 要點諗點諗就可以改善<br />\nWTF 明明好多問題係另一半做成<br />\n但冇人可以指出佢問題所在<br />\n反而不斷教我應該點做"},{"pid":"4d397842f38b3c8dc98f29538c99fc38a3a03e6f","tid":989620,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbf8f3c1af767c775782027bc485c5a25f35a25d","tid":989620,"uid":17245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:04:21.000Z","msg":"最撚慘係明明另一半迫到自己有情緒病<br />\n但睇醫生，社工，心理醫生都係著重話你有啲咩野問題 要點諗點諗就可以改善<br />\nWTF 明明好多問題係另一半做成<br />\n但冇人可以指出佢問題所在<br />\n反而不斷教我應該點做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:11:29.000Z","msg":"最經典係所謂啲社工<br />\n我老婆係社工面前不斷講我有啲咩野唔岩<br />\n佢自己做錯左既野就隻字不提<br />\n一次過講一大堆野出黎我都冇力氣每點駁佢<br />\n個社工居然同我講<br />\n你俾你老婆講曬去啦<br />\n佢唔講出黎到佢屈到病<br />\nWTF<br />\n有病食緊藥既坐左係你面前既<br />\n你又唔顧下我感受<br />\n<br />\n又唔係每樣野了解下個背景<br />\n一味問有咩野講就一次過講出黎<br />\n家下啲社工真係好撚好做"},{"pid":"abd933dde7abb86e53c8ace607887fd2ef64dfbe","tid":989620,"uid":205307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90f33b6dca63bec97e08d58682f849e3832b1666","tid":989620,"uid":75707,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:59:03.000Z","msg":"好撚煩 做錯乜撚野都賴落自己有病到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:12:42.000Z","msg":"係你另一半？咩病"},{"pid":"ac6d5faf4a3aeda710bbe7b63356d35c46098632","tid":989620,"uid":205307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbf8f3c1af767c775782027bc485c5a25f35a25d","tid":989620,"uid":17245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:04:21.000Z","msg":"最撚慘係明明另一半迫到自己有情緒病<br />\n但睇醫生，社工，心理醫生都係著重話你有啲咩野問題 要點諗點諗就可以改善<br />\nWTF 明明好多問題係另一半做成<br />\n但冇人可以指出佢問題所在<br />\n反而不斷教我應該點做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:13:20.000Z","msg":"我本身冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但俾另一半搞到有<br />\n巴打咩病？"},{"pid":"bea4d4e7fa445a3d1953e8cd225d92d45cf0d98b","tid":989620,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"唔好生仔 唔該你"},{"pid":"f0c8e201863f2ae57a04ff12effa3243b34a0750","tid":989620,"uid":205307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bea4d4e7fa445a3d1953e8cd225d92d45cf0d98b","tid":989620,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"唔好生仔 唔該你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:46:32.000Z","msg":"本身不孕 但都多謝提醒"},{"pid":"a27b4aef7df17d00e